title: You don't know why you came here
creator_credit: Dick Marks, Millie Williams and Martin Williams Films
brief_description: Trisha returns home to Queensland after years abroad. She travels through the state while a musical soundtrack provides a background to the scenery. No spoken commentary. Music by Terry Hannigan.
